{"tid":2217172,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"微信女早預告｜偉源洗倉式暴瀉94% 此前2個月炒高1.5倍","createTime":"2020-09-25T08:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T10:37:58.000Z","uid":323911,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c6192ff3066d0bb8aa09cc6ded968cde96024507","tid":2217172,"uid":323911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:54:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200925/CEZFXTRS65GVLMBTY3UWPXLCZY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyatm&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3mnIYL__T1j0pWhvzDqobJrOXDz0Iev8Vewa2yXulhYbUyDsgIO-1AAng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200925%2FCEZFXTRS65GVLMBTY3UWPXLCZY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyatm%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3mnIYL__T1j0pWhvzDqobJrOXDz0Iev8Vewa2yXulhYbUyDsgIO-1AAng&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzoZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=ce53b289\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200925%2FCEZFXTRS65GVLMBTY3UWPXLCZY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyatm%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3mnIYL__T1j0pWhvzDqobJrOXDz0Iev8Vewa2yXulhYbUyDsgIO-1AAng&h=38d45ba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200925/CEZFXTRS65GVLMBTY3UWPXLCZY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyatm&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3mnIYL__T1j0pWhvzDqobJrOXDz0Iev8Vewa2yXulhYbUyDsgIO-1AAng</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oTjALxL434UOdhrQusW72b3RRio=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J2HVTUYRT5GUXARLML3PIVLQUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoTjALxL434UOdhrQusW72b3RRio%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ2HVTUYRT5GUXARLML3PIVLQUY.jpg&h=788aaac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【更新股價】再有細價股股價暴瀉，偉源（1343）午後僅5分鐘由4元水平，急瀉9成至0.4元，收報0.236元，跌足94.12%，成交2.37億元。該股股價表現與「微信女」騙案有相似地方，股份自7月起徘徊1.5元水平，後逐步炒高4元水平，並於高位大成交派貨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rkhEcze9asNhPkKO3QukU_WMlas=/750x646/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QG4LFOJJ3ZBV5FRP2OZRNF5NFI.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrkhEcze9asNhPkKO3QukU_WMlas%3D%2F750x646%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQG4LFOJJ3ZBV5FRP2OZRNF5NFI.jpeg&h=e54c2f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有限生微信女本周三已預告，偉源將會大跌，料為博取信任舉動。讀者提供圖片。<br />\n<br />\n偉源為一間位於新加坡的承建商，並專門提供土木工程公用事業工程已逾28年。<br />\n<br />\n早前壹傳媒（282）股價大幅波動，警方高調拘捕15人，指他們涉及透過WhatsApp群組操控壹傳媒股價，被控以「串謀詐騙」及「處理已知道或相信為代表從可公訴罪行的得益的財產」，事件引起金融界譁然，惟一直未見跟進「微信女」騙案。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，證監會昨日推出facebook官方專頁，並提醒公眾注意，指越來越多騙徒利用社交媒體平台詐騙投資者。該會透露現，正調查的操縱市場個案中， 這些騙局約佔20%。"},{"pid":"e768b96b2181080c8db1f3ae97a5f0def05100a5","tid":2217172,"uid":323911,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:55:52.000Z","msg":"毒品調查科呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e8f9fefe1c69168868a3a9785b24d9fcf907e5","tid":2217172,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e768b96b2181080c8db1f3ae97a5f0def05100a5","tid":2217172,"uid":323911,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTim